Articles.Content:
My first scale replica plane. It is based of the C-130 cargo plane. It is made using B9, PWings, Modular MultiWheels, Firespitter, and MechJeb. Craft File: https://drive.google.com/file/d/0BwOcG3_E_tIpbkJGNU9DUWV2V2s/view?usp=sharing

http://imgur.com/a/tU6Kr
You can click the 'Insert Image' button and copy paste the link in it followed by a .png(without any spacing) and the picture will be shown directly on the forums.
Pretty good, but I think the wings are a bit too long.
